by stof at 2021-03-02T20:19:58Z

AFAIK, `shivammathur/setup-php` can install older PHP versions on ubunut-20-04. What changes is which pre-installed version is available.

The difference is that when a version is not pre-installed, properly configuring the list of extensions you need is more important (as there is no preinstalled extensions either). tests in https://github.com/symfony/maker-bundle/pull/828/checks?check_run_id=2016163291 are failing because they try to use PDO mysql without installing that extension.

